snippet.title: 'RHOSLC’ Star Meredith Marks Admits It’s ‘Not Fun’ Rewatching Jen Shah’s Arrest
snippet.description:
Meredith Marks looks back on the arrest of her "Real Housewives of Salt Lake City" co-star Jen Shah, while opening up about the the explosive second season of the show. Watch "The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City" Sundays at 9 p.m. ET/PT on Slice and Mondays on hayu.
